OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777482354
OL,3,CPolice dig at makeshift grave site
OL,4,Cwhere teenager's body was found
OL,6,FExcavations close to the makeshift
OL,7,Fgrave site where Kieran Williams was
OL,8,Ffound is part of an ongoing murder
OL,9,Finvestigation
OL,11,FPolice have begun digging at the
OL,12,Fmakeshift grave site where the body of
OL,13,Fa young man was discovered in
OL,14,FSunderland.
OL,16,FKieran Williams went missing from his
OL,17,Fhome in Sunderland on 18 April 2022
OL,18,Fand was found dead six weeks later in
OL,19,Fa grave on a disused industrial estate
OL,20,Fnear the River Wear.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777482354
OL,3,CPolice dig at makeshift grave site
OL,4,Cwhere teenager's body was found
OL,6,FThe 18-year-old had been stabbed at
OL,7,Fleast 23 times and his body set on
OL,8,Ffire before being dumped on land
OL,9,Fbetween the Northern Spire Bridge and
OL,10,FClaxheugh Rocks.
OL,12,FAs part of an ongoing murder
OL,13,Finvestigation, officers are carrying
OL,14,Fout a number of planned 'test
OL,15,Fexcavations' on Wednesday (29 April).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777482354
OL,3,CPolice dig at makeshift grave site
OL,4,Cwhere teenager's body was found
OL,6,FThe work, taking place in similar
OL,7,Fconditions and at the same time of
OL,8,Fyear as Kieran's disappearance, is
OL,9,Fhoped to help establish how long it
OL,10,Ftook to dig the grave and how many
OL,11,Fpeople it would have taken.
OL,13,FDetective Superintendent Matt Steel,
OL,14,Fthe Senior Investigating Officer for
OL,15,Fthe case, said:
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777482354
OL,3,CPolice dig at makeshift grave site
OL,4,Cwhere teenager's body was found
OL,6,F"As part of our ongoing activity,
OL,7,Fofficers and specialists are carrying
OL,8,Fout a number of planned test
OL,9,Fexcavations today (Wednesday) at the
OL,10,Fmakeshift grave site where Kieran's
OL,11,Fbody was found.
OL,13,F"This is located on a disused
OL,14,Findustrial estate South of the River
OL,15,FWear, between the Northern Spire
OL,16,FBridge and Claxheugh Rocks, in
OL,17,FSunderland.
OL,19,F"As a result, there is a cordon in
OL,20,Fplace, and an increased police
OL,21,Fpresence in the surrounding area.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777482354
OL,3,CPolice dig at makeshift grave site
OL,4,Cwhere teenager's body was found
OL,6,F"Please be assured that there is no
OL,7,Fwider risk to the public, and we'd
OL,8,Fcontinue to urge anyone who can assist
OL,9,Four investigation to do the right
OL,10,Fthing and get in touch with police."
OL,12,FThe excavations come just days after
OL,13,FNorthumbria Police renewed its appeal
OL,14,Ffor information - four years on from
OL,15,Fthe day the teenager went missing.
OL,17,FLouis Hackett and Ben Cook were
OL,18,Fcleared of his murder following a
OL,19,Ftrial at Newcastle Crown Court, but
OL,20,FHackett was convicted of manslaughter.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
